isn't working at this time,

24:51.404 --> 24:53.990
was manufactured in England by A.G. Hill.

24:55.325 --> 24:57.828
Did you hear the one about
the choir mistress and the minister?

24:59.579 --> 25:00.997
- No.
- She chased him

25:01.081 --> 25:02.916
around the church
and caught him by the organ.

25:05.043 --> 25:08.922
Huh. Oh, no, I hadn't heard that one.

25:09.381 --> 25:10.757
All right, come on. Follow me.

25:12.050 --> 25:14.093
All right, thank you all very much.

25:14.927 --> 25:16.011
- Be well.
- Thank you.

25:16.095 --> 25:18.054
Yeah, thanks a lot.

25:21.475 --> 25:22.601
Drive safe.

25:25.771 --> 25:26.689
Thanks.

